msgstr ""

#: .\npc\Refugee center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
msgid "Well, that’s bad.  Return if you change your mind."
msgstr ""

#: .\npc\Refugee center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
msgid "Try to look at the bar or in some lonely guy's house."
msgstr ""

#: .\npc\Refugee center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
msgid "Did you found any vodka?"
msgstr ""

#: .\npc\Refugee center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
msgid ""
"He-he.  I believed in you, pal.  *Berry took a large sip*  Here's the cash I"
" promised.  Spend it well, he-he."
msgstr ""

