" as a chance to break free.  And, um, I think the guy like him would "
"definitely try to take his revenge, so… I just want to know for sure if the "
"guy is alive or turned into <zombie>.  Find police records, so I can learn "
"where did they locked him, and maybe learn what happened to him there."
